query:
SELECT 
  rl.id,
  rl.contractorId,
  CONCAT(c.firstName, ' ', c.lastName) as contractorName,
  rl.reminderType,
  rl.sentAt,
  rl.responded,
  rl.respondedAt,
  rl.response
FROM reminderLogs rl
JOIN contractors c ON rl.contractorId = c.id
WHERE DATE(rl.sentAt) = CURDATE()
ORDER BY rl.sentAt DESC
